race.comment: A tough way to finish the card with quite a few winning chances. GRINZINGER HALO (10) has really found form with back-to-back wins. This is harder but she will roll forward and make her own luck. FEARLESS WRITER (5) has performed well so far this prep, settling back and catching the eye late in most of her runs. Will be doing the same here. Will have plenty of admirers however racing style makes her hard to follow and catch. SAVSONIC (9) is a top-three chance if she can repeat her first-up run. SHISUTA BO (4) doesn't run poorly at the moment and must be considered for wider plays. SACHEM (3) has improved with each run this campaign. Should be at his peak fourth up.
